The paper deals with processing non-uniform data signals of different topologies, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of CNNs for analyzing such signals also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a mathematical formulation for Non-Uniform Fourier Transforms (NUFT), which is a topic in numerical analysis (cs.NA) and signal processing (cs.SI).
